'''舊韋斯特伯里'''（'''Old Westbury'''） 是位於[[美國|美國]][[紐約州|紐約州]][[納蘇縣_(紐約州)|納蘇縣]]的一個村莊，據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，當地有4,671位居民。2007年《Business Week》雜誌將此地評為紐約生活費最高昂的郊區。<ref name="images.businessweek.com">{{Cite web |url=http://images.businessweek.com/ss/07/01/0124_suburbs/source/13.htm |title=Business Week, "The Most Expensive Suburbs of the Biggest U.S. Cities, New York City: Old Westbury" |access-date=2015-04-03 |archive-date=2014-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140722103128/http://images.businessweek.com/ss/07/01/0124_suburbs/source/13.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 當地的[[舊韋斯特伯里花園|舊韋斯特伯里花園]]在地區內頗有名氣，此外[[紐約科技學院|紐約科技學院]]在村裡有一個面積達{{convert|1050|acre|km2}}的校區。<ref name=snider>{{cite book|last1=Snider|first1=Mark D.|title=Colleges in New York|date=2009|publisher=[[Peterson's|Peterson's]]|isbn=0-7689-2692-0|page=63|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WbPMZanrgSYC&pg=PA63&lpg=PA63&dq=new+york+institute+of+technology+old+westbury+campus+old-+westbury+ny+acre&source=bl&ots=qnS_I2jvMH&sig=G69Wm_ty9vMolxitSVSOayL7xjI&hl=en&sa=X&ei=8dIMVZLTEe3IsQTRyYHIDQ&ved=0CB0Q6AEwADgK#v=onepage&q=new%20york%20institute%20of%20technology%20old%20westbury%20campus%20old-%20westbury%20ny%20acre&f=false|access-date=2015-04-03|archive-date=2016-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416092322/https://books.google.com/books?id=WbPMZanrgSYC&pg=PA63&lpg=PA63&dq=new+york+institute+of+technology+old+westbury+campus+old-+westbury+ny+acre&source=bl&ots=qnS_I2jvMH&sig=G69Wm_ty9vMolxitSVSOayL7xjI&hl=en&sa=X&ei=8dIMVZLTEe3IsQTRyYHIDQ&ved=0CB0Q6AEwADgK#v=onepage&q=new%20york%20institute%20of%20technology%20old%20westbury%20campus%20old-%20westbury%20ny%20acre&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

